16:17:47 <HarshPandit> ChristianDraeger: Yes, we should have this session and discussion
16:17:47 <HarshPandit> BeatrizEsteves: This issue of classes vs instances would be more prominent in OWL,  shouldn't that severe an issue with SKOS and RDF
16:17:47 <HarshPandit> JulianFlake: Yes, agree, we should have this session. Having two hierarchies called parent term and parent type can create issues with interpretation.
